      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center md:items-start md:justify-start lg:items-start lg:justify-start gap-4 bg-blueMain md:rounded-t-2xl p-8 md:h-full"
      >
        <div
          id="DrumMixer"
          class="scroll-mt-20 text-2xl md:text-4xl w-full text-center lg:text-start md:text-start"
        >
          <h1 class="text-redBg">TRIASO®</h1>
          <h1 class="">DRUM MIXER</h1>
        </div>
        <p
          class="text-grisSubP text-base md:text-lg text-center lg:text-justify md:text-justify"
        >
          Heavy-duty drum mixers engineered for continuous operation and precise
          asphalt blending. Built with heat-resistant alloy steel and optimized
          air-flow design, they achieve uniform drying, minimal fines loss, and
          maximum fuel efficiency — ensuring long service life and consistent
          performance under demanding conditions
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full bg-blueMain p-6">
      <h1 class="text-xl text-center md:text-start lg:text-start md:text-4xl">
        RANGING FROM 10 TO 500 TPH
      </h1>
    </div>
    <div class="block md:hidden">
      <Image src={img7} alt="Drum Mixer" class="w-1/2" />
      <div class="flex-col flex md:hidden items-start justify-start pt-4">
        <h1 class="md:text-4xl text-2xl text-black text-center w-full">
