        </h1>
        <br />
        <p class="md:text-2xl text-lg text-grisT text-center w-full">
          We stand behind our top-tier quality with the <br />
          highest warranty in the market
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center mt-20 text-black max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4"
  >
    <h1 class="text-xl md:text-3xl text-center md:mb-10">
      Asphalt plants for the smallest jobs to large projects
    </h1>

    <div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-black transform-gpu">
      <video
        class="block w-full h-auto object-cover transform-gpu will-change-transform [backface-visibility:hidden] bg-black"
