          loads, simplifying logistics and reducing setup time.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="grid max-w-7xl mx-auto grid-cols-1 px-8 space-y-5 lg:min-h-[300px] md:min-h-[300px] lg:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-2"
