            Integrated 5th wheel. Direct transport to site
          </h1>
          <div class="text-start pl-0 lg:pl-5 md:pl-5">
            <li class="font-thin">No lowbed or flatbed trailer.</li>
          </div>

          <p class="font-thin text-start lg:text-start md:text-start">
            The complete asphalt plant can be transported in <span
              class="font-bold">only three</span
            > trailer loads, simplifying logistics and reducing setup time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="flex flex-col justify-start items-start lg:justify-start lg:items-start md:justify-start md:items-start text-white space-y-2 pb-5"
        >
