          class="font-thin text-base text-center md:text-start lg:text-start lg:text-lg"
        >
          The drum collar is engineered to provide the controlled and efficient
          entry of Recycled Asphalt Pavement (RAP) into the mixing zone. Fed
          directly from the RAP bin via a dedicated conveyor, the material
          enters the drum smoothly and uniformly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 text-center">
      <p class="font-thin text-base lg:text-lg">
        For very 10% of RAP, <br />
        the cost of hot-mix production
      </p>
