      <p class="font-thin text-base lg:text-lg">
        By recycling up to 50% RAP woth our plants,<br />
        you can achieve approximately 35% savings in hot-mix production costs.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 flex flex-col lg:grid md:grid lg:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-2 py-10 gap-6"
