        <p
          class="text-sm text-[#2b2b2b] text-center lg:text-base lg:text-justify md:text-lg md:text-justify"
        >
          The pugmill is a optional component at the final stage of the drum-mix
          process, used when the hot mix design or project specifications
          require additional blending to meet uniformity requirements. Equipped
          with two heavy-duty shafts and precisely engineered mixing flights, it
          ensures complete homogenization and consistency throughout the
          material.
        </p>
        <Image
          src={img2}
          alt="Pugmill component for the drum-mix"
          class="block md:hidden my-4"
        />
      </div>
      <Image
        src={pugmill}
